graph TD
    User([User])
    KB["KnowledgeBase Component"]
    Content["KnowledgeContent Component"]

    subgraph Views
        Wiki[WikiView]
        Precedents[PrecedentsView]
        QA[QAView]
        Analytics[KnowledgeAnalytics]
    end

    UseQuery["React Query"]
    DataService["DataService Facade"]
    API_Knowledge["API: Knowledge"]
    Backend["NestJS Backend"]
    DB[(PostgreSQL)]

    User -->|Select Tab| KB
    KB -->|Active Tab| Content
    Content -->|Route| Wiki
    Content -->|Route| Precedents
    Content -->|Route| QA
    Content -->|Route| Analytics

    Wiki -->|getWikiArticles| UseQuery
    Precedents -->|getPrecedents| UseQuery
    QA -->|getQA| UseQuery
    Analytics -->|getAnalytics| UseQuery

    UseQuery -->|Call| DataService
    DataService -->|Call| API_Knowledge
    API_Knowledge -->|GET /knowledge/*| Backend
    Backend -->|Query| DB
    DB -->|Result| Backend
    Backend -->|Response| API_Knowledge
    API_Knowledge -->|Data| DataService
    DataService -->|Data| Views
    Views -->|Render| User